                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-167-off948 t18181028-167-crimeloc951"></join>. On the 17th of September, about three o'clock in the morning, the watchman alarmed me. I found I had lost the articles stated in the indictment out of my safe-the prisoner had formerly lived with me - He must have got in at the window.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18181028-167-person1131">
                  CHARLES 
                  WARNER
